<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/cqgssebastian/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u7409672-28.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cqgssebastian/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">weiwenjiang</span>
