      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="20927672">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Trovatore/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1028471-2.jpg" alt="Trovatore" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20927672/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20927672/" class="">入不二法门品第九</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Trovatore/" class=" " title="Trovatore">Trovatore</a>
                (我思我想我怕我会心意变灰)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20927672">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">于是文殊师利问维摩诘：“我等各自说已，仁者当说何等是菩萨入不二法门？”时维摩诘默然无言。文殊师利叹曰：“善哉！善哉！乃至无有文字语言，是真入不二法门。”
所谓不二法门，不垢不净，不增不减，非法非非法；说与不说，俱是讲经。佛说不二法门，即非不二法门，是名不二法门。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-09-07 12:54</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">2人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>于是文殊师利问维摩诘：“我等各自说已，仁者当说何等是菩萨入不二法门？”时维摩诘默然无言。文殊师利叹曰：“善哉！善哉！乃至无有文字语言，是真入不二法门。”</q></blockquote>
所谓不二法门，不垢不净，不增不减，非法非非法；说与不说，俱是讲经。佛说不二法门，即非不二法门，是名不二法门。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
